PREHEAT oven to 400 degrees F. COMBINE egg, ricotta cheese and salt in large bowl; whisk to blend. STIR in 1 1/2 cups seasoned cheese and chicken; spoon mixture equally into shells. SPRAY baking dish with nonstick cooking spray; spread 1 cup sauce in bottom of dish. ARRANGE stuffed shells in baking dish; top with remaining sauce. SPRINKLE remaining seasoned cheese over top; cover and bake for 30 minutes.